fontforge: fontforge (An outline font editor)
fontforge:
fontforge: FontForge allows you to edit outline and bitmap fonts. You can create
fontforge: new ones or modify old ones.  It is also a font format converter and
fontforge: can convert among PostScript (ASCII & binary Type 1, some Type 3s,
fontforge: some Type 0s), TrueType, OpenType (Type2), CID-keyed, SVG, CFF and
fontforge: multiple-master fonts.
